  "texts": [
    "In [70], the authors showed that parameterefficient fine-tuning (PEFT) with open-source 7-8B LLMs can outperform GPT-4 on domain-specific tasks by an average of 10 points.",
    "Several studies showed that the performance improvements obtained by fine-tuning exceed those gained through prompt engineering [71,72].The advantages and disadvantages of different customization methods with a pretrained LLM in are summarized in Table 1.",
